Privacy Policy for Time Tracker App
Effective Date: 23 December 2024

This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect the information provided by users of the Time Tracker App. Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to ensuring your information is secure and used responsibly.
1. Information We Collect

The Time Tracker App does not collect any personal or sensitive data from its users. The app is designed to provide a simple counting functionality without requiring any user input or account registration.
2. How We Use Your Data

As no user data is collected or stored by the app, there is no data usage.
3. Data Storage and Security

Since the app does not store or transmit user data, there are no storage or security concerns for personal information. However, if future updates include data tracking features, appropriate measures will be taken to secure user information.
4. Permissions

The app does not request any permissions to access your device's features or data.
5. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy in the future to include additional details if new features are added to the app. Users will be notified of any changes via app updates.
